TY  - JOUR
TI  - Intertemporal Utility Functions and the Long-Run Consumption Function
AU  - Thompson, Earl A.
AB  - [This paper asserts and demonstrates an equivalence that exists between the utility function implied by a general form of the standard aggregate consumption function and a subclass of the general class of additive utility functions used in the optimal savings literature.]
